title: Joan MacDonald
itunes:title: Joan MacDonald
description: At the age of 70, Joan MacDonald made the powerful decision to say YES to the help she was offered by her family. She overcame her health obstacles by committing to exercise and nutrition, and has inspired millions of people throughout her fitness journey. It’s never too late to reinvent.
